{"tid":1596450,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"十點鐘、我地一齊再嗌過好唔好","createTime":"2019-09-26T13:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T13:48:10.000Z","uid":276145,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"81c269569fcc22907adff51f9733ec29499eb2c2","tid":1596450,"uid":276145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:35:55.000Z","msg":"我地係唔係已經唔記得左十點鐘要嗌<br />\n嗌到呢場運動結束、香港人得到回應先至停<br />\n已經幾個禮拜無嗌過啦<br />\n岩岩一場咁嘅見面會個老虔婆答左啲乜野大家心照<br />\n你地得到嘅回應係乜野啊？<br />\n無啊、我屌你老母<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">爭氣少少啦香港人</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n十點鐘我要聽到有人嗌<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"ed9957d149dfc6fdb391930bc10dfabcfcbd5cb5","tid":1596450,"uid":16746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:36:38.000Z","msg":"黃大仙手足表示準備好"},{"pid":"ec14ec36c1bc8a473d311891d690e92326c79740","tid":1596450,"uid":276145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"我P牌推唔到po啊<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求缺一不可啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"1461261aad063695620fa1427dd130f9953a0132","tid":1596450,"uid":276145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:38:45.000Z","msg":"嗌啊<br />\n我叫你地嗌啊<br />\n我要你地嗌到我滿意為止啊"},{"pid":"d1412a0d0c9aa94f773819a9e2f515df6d2b7800","tid":1596450,"uid":308414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:39:29.000Z","msg":"gogogo"},{"pid":"9b56bbb507d558254678534dff183e162984200d","tid":1596450,"uid":169262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T13:40:52.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oq9Tz9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foq9Tz9f.jpg&h=dc0f42d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd4b4466e74403c61246bad85d43a43bfa1a1a8d","tid":1596450,"uid":258362,"like":0,"di